Class AbstractController<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • AbstractController<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Interface type of the associated view
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.util.EventListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AccountController, TransactionController

    public abstract class AbstractController<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener
    Base class for controller objects. Classes that inherit from AbstractController should specialize the template with the Interface type of the view it is associated with.
